item.title: My Third Post
item.description:
Training Plan

Day 1: (A few days post-flu) 20-30 minute easy-effort run. Day 2: Cross-train 30 minutes at an easy effort. Day 3: 30-minute easy-effort run. Day 4: Cross-train 30 minutes at an easy effort. Day 5: 40-minute easy-effort run. Day 6: Cross-train 30 minutes at an easy effort. Day 7: 60-minute easy-effort run. Day 8: Cross-train 40 minutes at an easy effort. Day 9: 45-minute easy-effort run. Day 10: Cross-train 45 minutes at a moderate effort. Day 11: 90-minute easy-effort run. Day 12: Cross-Ttrain 30-40 minutes at a moderate effort.
